## 1. Executive Summary

### What We're Building

An **Agent Intercom Protocol (AIP)** — a real-time, blocking inter-agent communication system that enables AI agents working on ads-related tasks to discover each other, ask questions, share context, and collaborate on complex workflows without human relay.

### Why

Today, our 12+ AI agents working across Ad Campaign Engine, DTC Strategy Agent, UMDM, Meta/Google Ads analyzers, CRO Agent, and Creative Factory all operate in isolation. When the Creative Scoring agent discovers a fatigued ad, it can't tell the Campaign Ops agent to pause it. When the DTC Strategy agent detects a growth stage change, it can't tell the Budget Optimizer to reallocate. Every cross-agent coordination requires a human to relay the message.

### Inspired By

Pi-Intercom (github.com/rtmendes/pi-intercom) — a local IPC messaging system for coding agents that implements blocking ask/reply, session discovery, and supervisor escalation. We're adapting its best patterns for our cloud-distributed, multi-app, Supabase-backed architecture.

### Target Apps (In Scope)

| App | Repo | URL | Backend |
|-----|------|-----|---------|
| Ad Campaign Engine | rtmendes/ad-campaign-engine | adengine.insightprofit.live | Convex (16 tables, 42 modules) |
| Offer Engine v3 | rtmendes/offer-stack-engine | offers.insightprofit.live | Convex (30+ tables) |
| Revenue Intelligence Engine | (Viktor Space) | revenue.insightprofit.live | Convex (15 tables) |
| Command Center v2 | rtmendes/insightprofit-command-v2 | command.insightprofit.live | Supabase + Next.js |
| UMDM (Data Layer) | (scripts + Supabase) | N/A (Supabase tables) | Supabase (10 tables) |

### Key Innovation Adopted from Pi-Intercom

| Pi-Intercom Pattern | Our Implementation |
|---------------------|-------------------|
| Unix socket broker | Supabase Realtime channel + `agent_intercom_messages` table |
| Blocking ask/reply (10-min timeout) | Supabase Realtime subscription with row-level notification + polling fallback |
| Session registry + presence | `agent_intercom_sessions` table with heartbeat |
| 3-tier supervisor escalation | Structured Slack escalation (BLOCKING → INTERVIEW → UPDATE) |
| Length-prefixed JSON framing | Typed JSON payloads in Supabase with Zod validation |
| Auto-spawn/auto-exit broker | Always-on Supabase (zero additional infrastructure) |

