## 6. CLAUDE.md for Coding Harness

This is the file that gets pushed to each repo for Claude Code / Codex / Cursor to follow.

```markdown
# CLAUDE.md — Agent Intercom Protocol Build Instructions

## Project Context
You are implementing the Agent Intercom Protocol (AIP) — a real-time inter-agent
communication system for InsightProfit's ads-related AI agents. This enables
agents across Ad Campaign Engine, Offer Engine, Revenue Intel Engine, and
Command Center to discover each other, send messages, ask blocking questions,
and escalate to human supervisors.

## Architecture
- **Data layer:** Supabase (self-hosted PostgreSQL + Realtime)
- **Client library:** TypeScript package `@insightprofit/agent-intercom`
- **App integration:** Convex actions call the client library
- **Dashboard:** Next.js component in Command Center v2
- **Escalation:** Supabase → Slack webhook → human response → Supabase

## Tech Stack (DO NOT change)
- Supabase (self-hosted) — PostgreSQL + Realtime + RLS
- Convex — backend for Ad Campaign Engine, Offer Engine, Revenue Intel
- Next.js 16 — Command Center v2 frontend
- TypeScript — all new code
- Tailwind CSS v4 — styling
- Zod — payload validation

## Key Files
- `schema.sql` — Supabase migration (4 tables, indexes, RLS, functions)
- `packages/agent-intercom/src/client.ts` — core client class
- `packages/agent-intercom/src/index.ts` — public exports
- `convex/agentIntercom.ts` — Convex action wrappers
- `src/views/AgentIntercomView.tsx` — dashboard component

## Critical Rules
1. NEVER delete existing files or tables — this is ADDITIVE only
2. NEVER modify existing Convex schema — add new modules alongside existing ones
3. All Supabase queries use service_role key (not anon key) from agent code
4. All Convex functions in agentIntercom.ts MUST be `"use node"` actions
5. Realtime subscriptions use `postgres_changes` channel, NOT broadcast
6. Polling fallback MUST exist for every Realtime subscription (3s interval)
7. All messages MUST be logged to agent_intercom_audit_log
8. Heartbeat interval: 30 seconds. Stale threshold: 2 minutes.
9. Ask timeout: 10 minutes default, configurable per-call
10. Escalation timeout: 10 minutes (blocking), 30 minutes (interview)

## Testing Commands
```bash
# Run client library tests
cd packages/agent-intercom && npx vitest run

# Run Convex functions locally
npx convex dev

# Test Supabase Realtime
npx ts-node scripts/test-realtime.ts

# Verify schema
psql $DATABASE_URL -f schema.sql --dry-run
```

## Done Criteria
- [ ] All 4 Supabase tables created with indexes and RLS
- [ ] expire_stale_asks() function deployed and tested
- [ ] Client library: connect, disconnect, send, ask, reply, broadcast, escalate all working
- [ ] Convex actions: sendMessage, askAgent, replyToAsk, listActiveSessions, escalateToHuman
- [ ] Dashboard shows live sessions, message timeline, escalation queue
- [ ] At least 2 agent-to-agent workflows tested end-to-end
- [ ] All tests passing
- [ ] No existing functionality broken
```

